export enum URI {
    USERS = 'http://localhost:3001/users',
    USER = 'http://localhost:3001/users/:uuid',
    DELETAR_USERS = 'http://localhost:3001/users/deletar/:uuid',
    CADASTRAR_USERS = 'http://localhost:3001/users/cadastrar',
    MODIFICAR = 'http://localhost:3001/users/modificar/:uuid'
}
